map <F2> :Gcommit<CR>
map <F3> :Gina push<CR>
imap <F1> <ESC>:w<CR>:Gadd<CR>i
imap <F2> <ESC>:Gcommit<CR>
imap <F3> <ESC>:Gina push<CR>i

